snippet.title: Slam And Roll - TRAILER. (Release on PC: 22nd May 2024)
snippet.description:
GET THE GAME: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2004960/Slam_and_Roll/?utm_source=KG&utm_medium=YT&utm_campaign=TRAILER6
Slam and Roll is coming to Steam May 22nd!

Join the sports club, defend planet Earth's monuments. Explore this arcade #retrogaming 16-bit platformer solo or team up with a friend.
